Interface Libvirt

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.sun.jna.Library

    public interface Libvirt
extends com.sun.jna.Library
    The libvirt interface which is exposed via JNA. The complete API is documented at http://www.libvirt.org/html/libvirt-libvirt.html.
